Class MenuItemTblImpl

    MenuItemTable
    public class MenuItemTblImpl
extends AbstractTable
implements MenuItemTable
    MenuItemTblImpl extends AbstractTable, implements the MenuItemTable interface, and permits limited access to the data stored in the menu_items table.
